Module gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib
Package gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client

Class CardHolderBiometricData

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client.PIVDataObject
      • gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client.SignedPIVDataObject
        • gov.gsa.pivconformance.cardlib.card.client.CardHolderBiometricData
  • public class CardHolderBiometricData
extends SignedPIVDataObject
    Container class that parses and stores information about Biometric Data elements. Biometric Data elements include Cardholder Fingerprints, Cardholder Facial Image and Cardholder Iris Image as defined by SP800-73-4 Part 2 Appendix A Table 11, Table 13 and Table 40
